<p>Naira estimates are based on a conversion rate of $1 to NGN 1,365 (CBN rate), with EUR to USD at approximately 1.10. These are estimates and will vary depending on the importer and exchange rate at the time of purchase.</p>



<p>Pre-orders are open from May 13, 2026. Every qualifying pre-order includes a free pair of Sony WH-1000XM6 noise-cancelling headphones during the launch window. Shipping begins June 26, 2026.</p>



